To build on Linux (Ubuntu/Debian),

1. ensure you have a C compiler and make

           apt-get install build-essential cmake

2. Make the build.sh script executable,

           chmod +x build.sh

3. Run the build script

			bash ./build.sh

To run the door, execute the following command

           ./slots [DROPFILE]

where [DROPFILE] is the full path and filename of door.sys dropfile. 

Ensure that the working directory is the MagiSlots directory.
